text: FX is an Bulgarian and Serbian pay television channel owned by Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA. The channel originally launched as Discovery Home & Health on 20 March 2013. On 4 December 2023, Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA announced that Discovery Home & Health in Bulgaria and the Balkans would be rebranded as FX on 6 March 2024. == Logos == file:Discovery H&H.png;|20 March 2013-6 March 2024 file:FX Logo 2023.svg|6 March 2024-present Category:Television channels in Europe
title: FX (Bulgarian and Serbian TV channel)
